  "title": "Chemical Technician / Chemical Processor - Experience Manufacturing/ 5Days",
  "description": "<ul><li>5 days work week (Office Hour)</li><li>Good Pay + Good Bonus + Good Allowance</li><li>Location at West/ North</li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>- Operate Reactor and mixing tanks to meet daily production targets</li><li>- Controlling and maintaining process parameters of Reactor</li><li>- Usage of flow meters and pumps to dose resins and solvents</li><li>- Use of drums to dose solvents</li><li>- Perform simple chemical analysis to check in-process quality</li><li>- Operate the grinding mills and mixing stirrer</li><li>- Operate pumps and filters to pack products into drums or IBC containers</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>- Prior experience in a manufacturing environment is a plus but not required</li><li>- Forklift license is mandatory</li></ul><p>Interested Candidates please send an updatedresume / CV in Ms Word format to click apply or Whatsapp your Resume detail to 98332779(SMS only without call).</p><p>Consulting in-charge :  Quah li lian (Registration no : R1983769)</p>",
